1em 0;">Getting SOC 2 certified requires companies to do a bunch of things.=
 According to <a href=3D"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkE2OwyAMhU9Td=
on4CSFZsJjNXCMi4KSoBCJwpurtx9MuRrKwjP384PMOYS_1Zc_SkP0dC75OsBmeLQEiVHY1qEsM=
